条件定义 
f(n) = 
\begin{cases} 
n/2,  & \mbox{if }n\mbox{ is even} \\ 
3n+1, & \mbox{if }n\mbox{ is odd} 
\end{cases}
多行等式、同余式 
\begin{align} 
f(x) & = (m+n)^2 \\
& = m^2+2mn+n^2 \\ 
\end{align} 
\begin{align} 
3^{6n+3}+4^{6n+3} 
& \equiv (3^3)^{2n+1}+(4^3)^{2n+1}\\   
& \equiv 27^{2n+1}+64^{2n+1}\\ 
& \equiv 27^{2n+1}+(-27)^{2n+1}\\ 
& \equiv 27^{2n+1}-27^{2n+1}\\ 
& \equiv 0 \pmod{91}\\ 
\end{align}
 
\begin{alignat}{3} 
f(x) & = (m-n)^2 \\ 
f(x) & = (-m+n)^2 \\ 
& = m^2-2mn+n^2 \\ 
\end{alignat}
多行等式（左对齐） 
\begin{array}{lcl} 
z        & = & a \\ 
f(x,y,z) & = & x + y + z  
\end{array}
多行等式（右对齐） 
\begin{array}{lcr} 
z        & = & a \\ 
f(x,y,z) & = & x + y + z 
\end{array}

-6x + 3y + 2z 
\end{cases}
